{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/blog/js-refresher-variables","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Javascript Refresher - Variables and data types","date":"2020-02-23"},"html":"<p>สวัสดีครับวันนี้จะมาเขียน blog เกี่ยวกับพื้นฐาน javascript เบื้องต้นนะครับ ช่วงนี้เรียนที่ codecamp เรื่องนี้พอดีเลยอยากจะทบทวนเก็บไว้อ่านสักหน่อย ที่จริงก็มีอยู่ใน <a href=\"https://github.com/xeusteerapat/javascript-refresher\">repository</a> ผมนี่แหละ แต่เป็นภาษาอังกฤษ (version ไม่แคร์ grammar 5555555) เนื้อหาก็เหมือนกันหมดเลยครับ (ก็ copy มานั่นแหละ 555555) ทำภาษาไทย เผื่อมีคนมาอ่าน</p>\n<p>เนื้อหาส่วนใหญ่จะอ้างอิงมาจาก</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript\">MDN JavaScript</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://javascript.info/\">The Modern JavaScript Tutorial</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.udemy.com/course/javascript-beginners-complete-tutorial/\">The Modern Javascript Bootcamp Course (2020)</a> ใครชอบดูเป็นวิดีโอแนะนำอันนี้เลยครับ เหมาะกับมือใหม่ เข้าใจง่าย</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong><em>ออกตัวก่อนนะครับว่าผมไม่ได้เก่งเลยยย ออกจะ beginner ด้วยซ้ำ เพียงแต่อยากเขียนเพื่อทบทวนความรู้ที่ได้รับมา ท่านใดเห็นว่าบทความผิด mention ผมที่ twitter ได้เลยครับ</em></strong></p>\n<h2>Variables declaration การประกาศตัวแปร</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>ใช้ <code>let</code> keyword.</li>\n<li>ใช้ <code>const</code> keyword.</li>\n<li>ใช้ <code>var</code> keyword.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><code>let</code> keyword</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">name</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Teerapat&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">name</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// prints &quot;Teerapat&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">myAge</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">33</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">myAge</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// prints &quot;33&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>การใช้ <code>let</code> keyword, เราสามารถอัพเดทค่าของตัวแปรได้ แต่ไม่สามารถประกาศตัวแปรเดิมซ้ำได้</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">myAge</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">33</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myAge</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk12\">myAge</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> + </span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">myAge</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// prints &quot;34&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\n<p><code>const</code> keyword (<code>const</code> stand for \"constant\")</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">pi</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">3.14159265359</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">gravity</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">9.8337</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>การใช้ <code>const</code> keyword, เราไม่สามารถอัพเดทค่าของตัวแปรได้</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"3\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">weight</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">68</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">weight</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> + </span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk3\">// TypeError: Assignment to constant variable.</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>การตั้งชื่อตัวแปรใน javascript นิยมใช้ \"camel case\" เช่น</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"4\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">myAge</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">33</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">resultWrapper</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk12\">document</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">getElementById</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;result&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2>Scoping rules</h2>\n<p>ในเว็บ Mozilla <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/let\">let keyword mozilla</a> อธิบาย scoping rules ซึ่งแตกต่างจาก <code>var</code> เอาไว้ว่า</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>Variables declared by let have their scope in the block for which they are defined, as well as in any contained sub-blocks.</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>ซึ่งการใช้ <code>var</code> ถึงแม้ว่าจะอยู่คนละ block scope แต่ก็ยังสามารถเข้าถึงตัวแปรได้ ซึ่งอาจจะก่อให้เกิดผลเสียที่ debug ได้ยากได้ แต่การใช้ <code>let</code> และ <code>const</code> จะถูก block ไว้ </p>\n<p>ตัวอย่างจาก MDN</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"5\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">function</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">varTest</span><span class=\"mtk1\">() {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">var</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">x</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// different scope</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk4\">var</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">x</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// same variable!</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">x</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 2</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">x</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 2</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">function</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">letTest</span><span class=\"mtk1\">() {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">x</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// different scope</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">x</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// different variable</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">x</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 2</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">x</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 1</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2>Data Types ประเภทของตัวแปร</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Primitive Types - ตัวแปรพื้นฐาน</li>\n<li>Object Types - ตัวแปรแบบวัตถุ</li>\n</ol>\n<p>ในที่นี้จะกล่าวถึงตัวแปรแบบ Primitive Types ก่อนนะครับ</p>\n<h2>Primitive Types</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Numbers</li>\n<li>String</li>\n<li>Boolean</li>\n<li>Null</li>\n<li>Undefined</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Numbers</h3>\n<p>ตัวเลขใน javascript จะเป็น type number หมดไม่ว่าเป็น integer หรือ float แม้กระทั่ง <code>Infinity</code> และ <code>NaN</code> (Not a Number)</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"6\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">myMoney</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">100</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">height</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">173.5</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> / </span><span class=\"mtk7\">0</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// Infinity</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">0</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> / </span><span class=\"mtk7\">0</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// NaN</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>เราสามารถตรวจสอบ type ของตัวแปรได้โดยใช้ <code>typeof</code> keyword.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"7\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">typeof</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">myMoney</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// &quot;number&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">typeof</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">height</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// &quot;number&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">typeof</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">Infinity</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// &quot;number&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">typeof</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">NaN</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// &quot;number&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\n<p><code>NaN</code> มันคือ \"Not a Number\" แต่ว่า <code>typeof NaN</code> คือ <code>\"number\"</code> อืมมมมมมมมมมม... ไอ่ตัวนี้ทำผมตกม้าตายไปหลายทีละ 555555</p>\n<h3>String</h3>\n<p>หรืออักขระนั่นเอง สามารถประไว้กายใต้ single quote หรือ double quotes ก็ได้</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"8\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">address</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;123 st. downtown&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">firstname</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;Teerapat&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Boolean</h3>\n<p>ตัวแปรประเภทตรรกกะ มีสองค่าคือ <code>true</code> กับ <code>false</code>.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"9\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">isChild</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk4\">true</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">isChecked</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk4\">false</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Null</h3>\n<p>ตัวแปรที่มีค่าเป็น <code>null</code> จะถูกใช้กับตัวแปรที่ไม่มีค่าใด ๆ เลย หรือตัวแปรที่เราไม่ทราบค่า</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It’s just a special value which represents “nothing”, “empty” or “value unknown”.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"10\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">myBox</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk4\">null</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Undefined</h3>\n<p>ความหมายของ <code>undefined</code> คือตัวแปรที่ยังไม่ถูกกำหนดค่าเข้าไป หรือว่าประกาศไปแล้วแต่ยังไม่ได้กำหนดค่าให้</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"11\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk4\">undefined</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">b</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">b</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// undefined</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>ความแตกต่างระหว่าง <code>null</code> กับ <code>undefined</code></h3>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"12\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">typeof</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">null</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// object (for legacy reasons)</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">typeof</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">undefined</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// undefined</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk3\">// also you can check</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">null</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> === </span><span class=\"mtk4\">undefined</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// false</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2>Operators ตัวดำเนินการ</h2>\n<p>บวก <code>+</code><br>\nลบ <code>-</code><br>\nคูณ <code>*</code><br>\nหาร <code>/</code><br>\nกำหนดค่า <code>=</code></p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"13\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk7\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> + </span><span class=\"mtk7\">3</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 5</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk7\">3</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> - </span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 2</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk7\">4</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> * </span><span class=\"mtk7\">6</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 24</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk7\">22</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> / </span><span class=\"mtk7\">7</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 3.142857142857143</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>ถ้าเราใช้ <code>+</code> กับ <code>string</code> เราจะได้ข้อความที่ต่อกัน</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"14\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">firstname</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Teerapat&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">lastname</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Prommarak&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">fullname</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk12\">firstname</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> + </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot; &quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> + </span><span class=\"mtk12\">lastname</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// Teerapat Prommarak</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>ถ้าเราใช้ <code>+</code> กับ <code>strings</code> และ <code>number</code>, มันจะต่อกันกลายเป็น <code>string</code> โดยอัตโนมัติ</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"15\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> + </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;2&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// &quot;12&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Shortened assigned การกำหนดค่าโดยเขียนแบบย่อ</h3>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"16\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">num</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">num</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> += </span><span class=\"mtk7\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// equal num = num + 2</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Other operators ตัวดำเนินการประเภทอื่น ๆ</h3>\n<p>Remainder <code>%</code>  การหาเศษจากการหาร<br>\nPower <code>**</code> การยกกำลัง</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"17\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk7\">10</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> % </span><span class=\"mtk7\">3</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 1</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk7\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> ** </span><span class=\"mtk7\">3</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 8</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Operator precedence ลำดับการดำเนินการก่อนหลังของตัวดำเนินการ</h3>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"18\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk7\">3</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> + </span><span class=\"mtk7\">4</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> / </span><span class=\"mtk7\">5</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 3.8 (just like 3 + (4 / 5))</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk7\">9</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> * </span><span class=\"mtk7\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> - </span><span class=\"mtk7\">7</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 11</span></span></code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/Operator_Precedence\">see more</a></p>\n<h3>Increment and Decrement</h3>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"19\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">count</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">10</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">count</span><span class=\"mtk1\">++;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">consol</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">count</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 11</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">num</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">12</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">num</span><span class=\"mtk1\">--; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 11</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">consol</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">num</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 11</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Logical operators ตัวดำเนินการประเภทตรรกะ</h3>\n<p>และ <code>&#x26;&#x26;</code><br>\nหรือ <code>||</code><br>\nไม่ <code>!</code></p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"20\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">true</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> && </span><span class=\"mtk4\">true</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// true</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">true</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> && </span><span class=\"mtk4\">false</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// false</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">false</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> && </span><span class=\"mtk4\">false</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// false</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">true</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> || </span><span class=\"mtk4\">true</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// true</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">true</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> || </span><span class=\"mtk4\">false</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// true</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">false</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> || </span><span class=\"mtk4\">false</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// false</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">!</span><span class=\"mtk4\">true</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// false</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">!</span><span class=\"mtk4\">null</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// false</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">!(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">3</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> &lt;= </span><span class=\"mtk7\">4</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// false</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2>Types Conversion การเปลี่ยนประเภทของตัวแปร</h2>\n<h3>Numeric conversion เปลี่ยนเป็น number</h3>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"21\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">num</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;123&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 123 as string</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">realNum</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk10\">Number</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">num</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 123 as number</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>String conversion เปลี่ยนเป็น string</h3>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"22\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">isCorrect</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk4\">true</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// boolean</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">isCorrectString</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk10\">String</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">isCorrect</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// &quot;true&quot; as string</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Boolean conversion เปลี่ยนเป็น boolean</h3>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"23\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk10\">Boolean</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// true</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk10\">Boolean</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">0</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// false</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk10\">Boolean</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;hi&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// true</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk10\">Boolean</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">) ; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// false</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2>String Methods วิธีการจัดการกับ string แบบต่าง ๆ</h2>\n<h3>String Indices</h3>\n<p>string จะมีดัชนี (index), ในแต่ละตัวอักษรเราสามารถเข้าถึงได้โดยใช้ index</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>s</th>\n<th>t</th>\n<th>r</th>\n<th>i</th>\n<th>n</th>\n<th>g</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>การใช้ <code>str.length</code> จะคืนค่าจำนวนตัวอักษร</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"24\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;My Stupid Mouth&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk12\">length</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 16, spaces include.</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Accessing characters การเข้าถึงแต่ละตัวอักษร</h3>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"25\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavsong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">[</span><span class=\"mtk7\">0</span><span class=\"mtk1\">]; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// M</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavsong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">[</span><span class=\"mtk7\">2</span><span class=\"mtk1\">]; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// &#39; &#39; space</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavsong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">[</span><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk12\">lenght</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> - </span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">]; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// h , last character</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Strings are immutable</h3>\n<p>ตัวแปรประเภท string ไม่สามารถเปลี่ยนค่าได้</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"26\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;My Stupid Mouth&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">[</span><span class=\"mtk7\">0</span><span class=\"mtk1\">] = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;D&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">console</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">log</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// still &quot;My Stupid Mouth&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Uppercase and Lowercase การเปลี่ยนเป็นตัวพิมพ์ใหญ่ พิมพ์เล็ก</h3>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"27\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;My Stupid Mouth&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">toUpperCase</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// &#39;MY STUPID Mouth&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">toLowerCase</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// &#39;my stupid Mouth&#39;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Getting a substring การเข้าบางส่วนของ string</h3>\n<p>สามารถใช้ <code>str.slice(start, [end])</code> โดยที่ตัวเลขสุดท้ายจะไม่ถูกรวมเข้าไป</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"28\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;My Stupid Mouth&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">slice</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">3</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk7\">9</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// &#39;Stupid&#39; space not include</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSons</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">slice</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">11</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// Mouth from 11 till the end</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Search for substring การหาตำแหน่งของอักขระ</h3>\n<p>ใช้ <code>str.indexOf</code> ถ้าไม่เจอ จะคืนค่าเป็น -1</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"29\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">indexOf</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Mouth&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 10</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">indexOf</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;TEAM&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// -1 if not found</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>includes, startWith and endsWith</h3>\n<p>การค้นหาอักษรบางส่วนใน string สามารถใช้ <code>includes</code> ได้ แต่วิธีนี้จะคืนค่าเป็น boolean<br>\nการใช้ <code>startWith</code> จะเป็นการตรวจสอบว่าขึ้นต้นด้วย ... หรือไม่<br>\nการใช้ <code>endWith</code> จะเป็นการตรวจสอบว่าลงท้ายด้วย ... หรือไม่</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"30\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">includes</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Mouth&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// true</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">includes</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;TEAM&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// false</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">startWith</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;My&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// true</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">endsWith</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Yes&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// false</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Trimming white space การลบช่องว่างใน string</h3>\n<p>สามารถใช้ <code>str.trim()</code> แต่จะลบเฉพาะหัวกับท้ายเท่านั้น</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"31\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">song</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;      Back To You       &quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">song</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">trim</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// &#39;Back To You&#39; spaces between are not remove</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>Replace การแทนที่ด้วย string อื่น</h3>\n<p>สามารถใช้ <code>replace</code></p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"32\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">let</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;My Stupid Mouth&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk12\">myFavSong</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">replace</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;My&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Your&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">//&#39;Your Stupid Mounth&#39;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2>Math Object การใช้ฟังก์ชั่นคณิตศาสตร์</h2>\n<p>มีวิธีการใช้ที่เป็นที่นิยมดังต่อไปนี้</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"33\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">Math</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.PI; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 3.141592653589793</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">Math</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">floor</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">5.8</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 5 ปัดทศนิยมทิ้งไม่ว่าจะเป็นเท่าไหร่</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">Math</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">round</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">5.4</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 5, ปัดตามหลักคณิตศาสตร์ ถ้าเป็น 5.5 หรือมากกว่าก็จะได้ 6</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">Math</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">ceil</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">5.1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 6 ปัดทศนิยมขึ้น</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">Math</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">abs</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(-</span><span class=\"mtk7\">123</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 123</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">Math</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">pow</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">3</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk7\">6</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 729, เหมือนกับ 3 ** 6</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">Math</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">random</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// สุ่มตัวเลขตั้งแต่ 0 ถึง 1</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk3\">// example for dice rolling</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk10\">Math</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">floor</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk10\">Math</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">random</span><span class=\"mtk1\">() * </span><span class=\"mtk7\">6</span><span class=\"mtk1\">) + </span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">; </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// result from 1 to 6</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>parseInt and parseFloat</h3>\n<p>ใช้สำหรับแปลงค่าเป็น number</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"34\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk11\">parseInt</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;24&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 24</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk11\">parseInt</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;24.54&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// get only 24</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk11\">parseFloat</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;24.54&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 24.54</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk11\">parseFloat</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;2dsfsdf&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 2</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk11\">parseInt</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Deeeee&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// NaN</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>สำหรับเนื้อหาบทนี้ ก็ขอจบไว้เท่านี้ก่อนนะครับ ไว้จะมาต่อเรื่อย ๆ ครับผม (ถ้ามีเวลา จะพยายามมี 55555555)</p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: inline-block;\n    min-width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: inline-block;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-highlighted {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-background-color, transparent);\n    box-shadow: inset var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width, 4px) 0 0 0 var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color, transparent);\n  }\n  \n  .dark-default-dark {\n    background-color: #1E1E1E;\n    color: #D4D4D4;\n  }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk4 { color: #569CD6; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk1 { color: #D4D4D4; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk12 { color: #9CDCFE; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk8 { color: #CE9178; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk10 { color: #4EC9B0; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk11 { color: #DCDCAA; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk3 { color: #6A9955; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk7 { color: #B5CEA8; }\n</style>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"js-refresher-variables"}}}